missionEventData.data1: Red 1 head to the jump point.

The captain of the Bixby, an Imperial Corvette that recently defected to the Rebel Alliance, has confirmed reports that the Empire is planning a major offensive in this sector of Rebel space. He believes that a large imperial fleet will begin its campaign in the Dellalt system. In your A-Wing, you will undertake a scouting patrol to look for this fleet. Scan all craft, do not engage the enemy.

missionEventData.data2: In the far reaches of the Outer Rim a rebellion is forming. A rebel cell led by the frigate Redemption and ace pilot Keyan Farlander have been striking back against the evil galactic empire. But the Emperor is at the height of his power, and even now he is marshalling his forces at the edge of the mid-rim. But help has come from the most unlikely of places. The captain of an imperial corvette has sent the rebel freedom fighters a secret message, he wishes to defect...

missionEventData.data1: Interesting. I'm not reading any ships.
Wait! Two freighters are entering the area.
This must be the beginning of the fleet. I'm going to move in and scan them.
Unidentified fighter. This is a restricted area. Clear the area at once.
Sorry buddy, but I need a closer look.
Detecting four Lancer Class Frigates exiting Hyperspace. Moving in to scan them.
Another group of Frigates is exiting.
Two more groups of Frigates are exiting. This isn't just a scouting party.
Looks like I've really kicked up the hornets nest.
Two Imperial Frigates have entered the area. I'm moving in to scan them then I'm going to jump home.
And that's a Victory Class Star Destroyer. Time to get out of here...

missionEventData.data3: Thanks to your exceptional flying weve got a good idea of the size of the imperial fleet and the sort of operation they are planning, unfortunately its not good news for us

missionEventData.data1: Select the ship then move in close to scan it
